### Verification
1. Run local automatic test runs using `pytest` to verify API and Storage lifecycles with the updated enums.
2. Manually test adding notes using the chat input console (e.g., `GOAL | Release alpha program | alpha | Test deployment`) and verify correctness of auto-classification.
3. Toggle to the Knowledge Graph view, verify nodes render with accurate colors matching their bucket allocations, drag nodes, and hover to see metadata tooltip popups.
4. Double-click on any node to verify it takes the user back to the chat feed and filters to show only that item.

