### Decisions
- **Includes**: Generalist terminology migration, auto-migrations on DB start, physics-based canvas graph implementation, FTS5-based Karpathy-style contextual chat RAG, and inline link highlighting.
- **Excludes**: Creating multi-database workspaces or third-party web cloud hosting for the knowledge map (we preserve 100% offline, speed-first single file architecture).

